EAs%20a%20single%20mom%2C%20I%20was%20particularly%20grateful%20for%20the%20support.%20She%20doted%20on%20her%20grandson%2C%20and%20the%20feeling%20was%20mutual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d693f2c-2636-4717-82da-47ee41918b7a%5C%22%3EMom%20began%20to%20get%20forgetful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20a%20former%20softball%20coach%20who%20has%20always%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-secrets-long-life-listening-keeping-busy-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprioritized%20her%20health%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20she%20started%20to%20act%20out%20of%20character.%20She%20began%20to%20experience%20forgetfulness%20and%20become%20easily%20irritated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20few%20times%20when%20she'd%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20you%20bring%20Braxton%20over%3F%20I%20want%20to%20see%20him.%26quot%3B%20When%20I%20did%2C%20she'd%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20y'all%20doing%20here%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20about%20caring%20for%20or%20living%20with%20relatives%20from%20a%20different%20generation%3F%20Please%20send%20details%20to%20jridley%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20go%20out%20to%20eat%2C%20and%20she'd%20get%20angry%20with%20the%20wait%20staff%20for%20no%20reason.%20Then%20she'd%20start%20crying%20out%20of%20the%20blue.%20She'd%20never%20behaved%20that%20way%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22947%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20women%20stand%20with%20a%20young%20boy%20outside%20a%20restaurant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6924d60c89026fbb4d0e5209%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22710%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScott%20said%20her%209-year-old%20son%20dotes%20on%20his%20grandmother.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lamia%20Scott%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20to%20worry%20about%20her%20safety%20after%20smel