d%20to%20warn%20them'%3A%20Elon%20Musk%20says%20Tesla's%20rivals%20don't%20want%20its%20self-driving%20tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6837b131ca50259add4d4308%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20stepping%20back%20from%20DOGE%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20spend%20less%20money%20on%20politics%20in%20the%20future.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%26quot%3B%20that%20none%20of%20Tesla's%20rivals%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20its%20self-driving%20tech.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETesla%20has%20been%20talking%20about%20licensing%20its%20Full%20Self-Driving%20tech%20for%20years.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFSD%20has%20faced%20scrutiny%2C%20with%20regulators%20launching%20a%20probe%20after%20reports%20of%20Teslas%20running%20red%20lights.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20can't%20understand%20why%20Tesla's%20rivals%20don't%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20its%20self-driving%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20CEO%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20other%20automakers%20aren't%20interested%20in%20licensing%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-fsd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFull%20Self-Driving%20(FSD)%3C%2Fa%3E%20software%2C%20despite%20his%20warnings%20that%20they%20risk%20dying%20out%20without%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20tried%20to%20warn%20them%20and%20even%20offered%20to%20license%20Tesla%20FSD%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20want%20it!%20Crazy%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Musk%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20legacy%20auto%20does%20occasionally%20reach%20out%2C%20they%20tepidly%20