Fbitcoin-price-why-is-crypto-down-btc-margin-calls-fed-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebitcoin's%20current%20pullback%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20now%20amounts%20to%20more%20than%2030%25%20from%20its%20recent%20all-time%20high%2C%20is%20different%20than%20prior%20declines%2C%20and%20could%20be%20more%20difficult%20to%20recover%20from%2C%20Deutsche%20Bank%20analysts%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeutsche%20Bank%20cited%20a%20couple%20of%20factors%20that%20distinguish%20the%20current%20bear%20market.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20prior%20crashes%2C%20driven%20primarily%20by%20retail%20speculation%2C%20this%20year's%20downturn%20has%20occurred%20amid%20substantial%20institutional%20participation%2C%20policy%20developments%2C%20and%20global%20macro%20trends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20big%20thing%20the%20bank%20flags%20is%20that%20adoption%20is%20stalling.%20According%20to%20the%20bank%2C%20crypto%20usage%20is%20down%20to%2015%25%20of%20retail%20traders%20from%2017%25%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20important%20because%20steadily%20widening%20adoption%20and%20use%20of%20bitcoin%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fundamental%20drivers%20behind%20its%20bull%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20crypto's%20underperformance%20also%20resurfaces%20our%20'Tinkerbell%20effect'%20theory%20that%20Bitcoin's%20valuations%20depend%20partly%20on%20belief-driven%20adoption%2C%26quot%3B%20analyst%20Marion%20Laboure%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20this%20correction%2C%20the%20'Tinkerbell%20effect'%20is%20prevalent%20as%20sentiment-driven%20selling%20has%20reinforced%20the%20price%20decline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20reason%20the%20latest%20plunge%20could%20be%20different%20is%20that%20institutional%20investors%20are%20now%20exposed%20to%20bitcoin%20through%20ETFs.%20The%20first%20bitcoin%20ETFs%20were%20approved%20in%20January%202024%2C%20which%20kicked%20off%20a%20600%25%20rally%20in%20the%20asset.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20decline%20of%20at%20least%2030%25%20in%20bitcoin's%20price%20since%20the%20funds%20began%20trading.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20institutional%20participation%20has%20boosted%20gains%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20it's%20that%20very%20same%20exposure%20to%20bitcoin%20that%20has%20also%20now%20contributed%20to%20a%20feedback%20loop%20of%20falling%20liquidity%20and%20heightened%20selling%2C%20DB%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20means%20it%20could%20be%20tougher%20for%20the%20apex%20cryptocurrency%20to%20pull%20itself%20out%20of%20its%20latest%20slump.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThinning%20liquidity%20across%20Bitcoin%20order%20books%20has%20limited%20the%20crypto's%20ability%20to%20significantly%20recover%20from%20macro%20headwinds%2C%26quot%3B%20Deutsche%20Bank%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20Bitcoin%20stabilizes%20after%20this%20correction%20remains%20uncertain%2C%26quot%3B%20Laboure%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BLooking%20ahead%2C%20Bitcoin's%20maturation%20will%20likely%20continue%20in%20phases.%20Greater%20regulatory%20clarity%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20from%20recent%20crypto%20market%20structure%20reforms%20%E2%80%94%20could%20support%20institutional%20confidence%2C%20while%20the%20adoption%20of%20stablecoins%20by%20major%20institutions%20may%20bolster%20market%20liquidity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-crash-reasons-why-different-from-prior-bear-market-declines-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764066601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6924aeec89026fbb4d0e4c28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-crash-reasons-why-different-from-prior-bear-market-declines-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bitcoin's%20current%20pullback%2C%20a%20more%20than%2030%25%20drop%20from%20recent%20highs%2C%20is%