ss%20Insider.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20is%20the%20easiest%20way%20to%20find%20information%20and%20has%20the%20least%20amount%20of%20friction%20will%20be%20most%20likely%20to%20be%20used%20for%20the%20particular%20search%20cases%2C%20whether%20it's%20voice%2C%20or%20text%2C%20or%20images%2C%26quot%3B%20Canaves%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b983b65a-5746-48d3-852c-3b80c900feca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20search%20is%20transforming%20Pinterest's%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPinterest%20has%20rolled%20out%20a%20series%20of%20revamped%20search%20tools%20under%20Ready's%20watch%2C%20including%20an%20AI-powered%20tool%20that%20enables%20users%20to%20discover%20content%20tailored%20to%20their%20body%20type%2C%20skin%20tone%2C%20and%20hair%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20platform%20expanded%20its%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-pinterest-visual-search-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisual%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20features%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20find%20exact%20products%20or%20similar%20items.%20It's%20a%20category%20that%20competitors%20like%20Google%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20new%20startups%20are%20also%20targeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20it%20works%3A%20Imagine%20you're%20redecorating%20your%20apartment%20and%20save%20an%20image%20for%20inspiration%20to%20your%20Pinterest%20board.%20With%20visual%20search%2C%20you%20can%20shop%20right%20from%20that%20image%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0clicking%20on%20a%20lamp%2C%20for%20example%2C%20will%20surface%20links%20to%20similar%20items%20and%20sometimes%20an%20exact%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20stronger%20search%20tools%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20data%20that%20comes%20with%20them%20%E2%80%94%20Pinterest%20has%20opened%20up%20more%20doors%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpinterest-targets-tiktok-advertisers-pitch-deck-full-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadvertisers%20and%20in-app%20shopping%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower-funnel%20ads%2C%20meaning%20ads%20that%20drive%20the%20user%20to%20make%20a%20purchase%2C%20make%20up%20two-thirds%20of%20Pinterest's%20business%2C%20Ready%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSearch%20behaviors%20are%20key%20inputs%20powering%20its%20ads%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Forrester%20analyst%20Evelyn%20Mitchell-Wolf%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat%20intel%20makes%20Pinterest%20a%20really%20attractive%20high-intent%20surface%20for%20advertisers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20also%20playing%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20how%20users%20shop%20via%20Pinterest%20by%20learning%20their%20tastes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEffectively%2C%20what%20we've%20created%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20shopping%20assistant%2C%26quot%3B%20Ready%20said.%20In%20October%2C%20Pinterest%20officially%20launched%20a%20shopping%20assistant%20tool%20that%20users%20can%20chat%20with%20verbally%20or%20over%20text.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20who%20visit%20Pinterest%20to%20search%2C%20whether%20for%20shopping%20or%20inspiration%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bmore%20valuable%26quot%3B%20than%20pass-by%20scrollers%2C%20said%20Kamran%20Ansari%2C%20Pinterest's%20former%20head%20of%20corporate%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20reason%20why%20Google%20built%20a%20%243%20trillion%20company%20is%20search%20has%20the%20highest%20kind%20of%20intent%20signal%20of%20anything%20you%20can%20possibly%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Ansari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226aba02e1-cdb9-4ffa-bb39-01415d2d1cf8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20search%20is%20'up%20for%20grabs'%20more%20than%20ever%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReady%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20Google%20for%20a%20little%20over%20two%20years%20before%20joining%20Pinterest%2C%20is%20well%20acquainted%20with%20the%20stakes%20in%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20still%20owns%20about%2090%25%20of%20the%20market%20share%20for%20traditional%20search%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20C