%20scientist%20at%20software%20company%20Thoughtworks%2C%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%23american-airlines-is-cutting-management-and-support-staff-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emassive%20job%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20tech%20world%20are%20one%20sign%20that%20the%20software%20development%20world%20is%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdepression.%26quot%3B%20In%20this%20current%20era%20of%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20businesses%20aren't%20investing%20in%20software.%20And%2C%20while%20the%20tech%20world%20is%20pouring%20money%20into%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20that%20growth%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bseparate%20thing%26quot%3B%20that's%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20bubbly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20businesses%20aren't%20investing%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20make%20much%20progress%20in%20the%20software%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Fowler%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20we%20have%20this%20weird%20mix%20of%20no%20investment%2C%20pretty%20much%20depression%20in%20the%20software%20industry%2C%20with%20an%20AI%20bubble%20going%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bunpredictable%26quot%3B%20AI%20bubble%20presents%20challenges%20and%20uncertainty%20for%20junior%20software%20engineers%2C%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20with%20bubbles%20is%20you%20never%20know%20how%20big%20they're%20going%20to%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20Fowler%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20know%20how%20long%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20before%20they%20pop%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20know%20what's%20going%20to%20be%20after%20the%20pop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20advice%20for%20junior%20software%20engineers%2C%20Fowler%20didn't%20discourage%20them%20from%20using%20AI%20for%20coding.%20However%2C%20he%20said%2C%20newer%20developers%20can't%20always%20identify%20if%20the%20output%20of%20large%20language%20models%2C%20or%20LLMs%20for%20short%2C%20is%20useful.%20That's%20where%20the%20knowledge%20of%20a%20more%20experienced%20coder%20comes%20in%20handy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20best%20way%20for%20junior%20developers%20to%20learn%20is%20to%20find%20a%20senior%20engineer%20to%20mentor%20them.%20A%20good%20experienced%20mentor%20is%20%26quot%3Bworth%20their%20weight%20in%20gold%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFowler%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20a%20pioneer%20in%20the%20field%20of%20software%20engineering.%20He%20was%20one%20of%2017%20authors%20of%20the%202001%20%26quot%3BAgile%20Manifesto%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20redefined%20how%20software%20is%20built%20collaboratively%20by%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20seemed%20confident%20in%20his%20industry%20to%20persevere.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20said%20the%20timing%20for%20software%20engineers%20starting%20out%20in%20tech%20may%20not%20be%20as%20great%20as%20it%20was%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20Fowler%20said%20there's%20%26quot%3Bplenty%20of%20potential%20in%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20core%20skills%20required%20of%20a%20good%20software%20engineer%20remain%20the%20same%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20AI%20is%20going%20to%20wipe%20out%20software%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20Fowler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartin-fowler-software-engineering-pioneer-advice-to-junior-developers-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764064861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6924c57289026fbb4d0e4f13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartin-fowler-software-engineering-pioneer-advice-to-junior-developers-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20uncertain%20times%20of%20AI%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bdepression%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20software%20world%2C%20Martin%20Fowler%20has%20advice%20for%20new%20coders.%22%