their%20barren%20lands%20%3C%2Fa%3Eimagining%20themselves%20as%20the%20man%20in%20the%20advertisement.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20curious%20about%20the%20crop%2C%20but%20I%20also%20had%20doubts%20about%20it.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20the%20office%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20market.%20I%20asked%20to%20be%20told%20about%2010%20such%20farmers%20who%20earned%20lakhs%20from%20aloe%20vera.%20The%20local%20officials%20got%20angry%20and%20threw%20me%20out%20of%20the%20office%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20harvesting%20period%20came%20in%2C%20Hrushikesh%20says%2C%20the%20businessman%20had%20run%20away.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20a%20fraud.%20I%20saw%20farmers%20crying.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20any%20strategy%20to%20market%20the%20crop%2C%20so%20they%20started%20clearing%20their%20fields%20and%20some%20threw%20them%20on%20roads%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20Interestingly%2C%20Hrushikesh%20picked%20the%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20and%20planted%20them%20in%20his%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20took%20him%20on%20a%20path%20which%20led%20him%20to%20establishing%2C%20what%20is%20today%2C%20a%20multi-crore%20company!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20started%20by%20planting%204%2C000%20discarded%20aloe%20vera%20plants%20on%20his%20field.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-2_11zon-1723013984-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu